  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.webm?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.mp4?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Save the Pirate! is an adventure game about a funny pirate, containing logical tasks. The main character must escape the dungeon, return his ship, and save his beloved. Take part in dangerous adventures with the Hero and determine his fate, but be careful – one wrong choice and you become a shark bait!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.webm?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.mp4?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game's storyline contains bonus levels and different options for the walkthrough with references to popular games and movies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/f5603dc39054efcac6ff015fcbd6ef0b.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/f5603dc39054efcac6ff015fcbd6ef0b.webm?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/f5603dc39054efcac6ff015fcbd6ef0b.mp4?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The fate of the characters in each chapter and mega final will depend on the player's decisions during the game.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.webm?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/fa82888636aa52522947c1fb3584d1c4.mp4?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Save the Pirate! is an adventure game about a funny pirate, containing logical tasks. The main character must escape the dungeon, return his ship, and save his beloved. Take part in dangerous adventures with the Hero and determine his fate, but be careful – one wrong choice and you become a shark bait!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.webm?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/20c0f73eee129aef78cd284e1bd00fe2.mp4?t=1737667778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game's storyline contains bonus levels and different options for the walkthrough with references to popular games and movies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442240/extras/f5603dc39054efcac6ff015fcbd6ef0b.poster.avif?t=1737667778\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.